{"tid":1936520,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"721 時序懶人包 屌你老母得6個人被控暴動罪","createTime":"2020-03-21T09:28:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T09:44:09.000Z","uid":69289,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f6ddcfb48b383a4a7b75347862be84c5741bb5c5","tid":1936520,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T09:28:10.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">721 時序懶人包 (Wikipedia)</div><br />\n1 雞地（晚上7時至10時）<br />\n2 白衫人首度入站襲擊（晚上10時至11時）<br />\n3 警方到場（晚上11時）<br />\n4 白衫人再度入站（晚上11時至凌晨12時）<br />\n5 白衣人在南邊圍村聚集（凌晨1時至5時）<br />\n6 市民到警署集體報案（凌晨1時至2時）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：當時凌晨睇直播，過百近千防暴入晒天水圍元朗，疊晒馬以為會捉晒幾百個白衫佬 (即係依家最興圍捕返狗屋)，點知第二朝成班收晒隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我仲諗緊係咪錯過咗啲新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"741c80d5c5a087cc5cecab8b5d15a6b2e4229373","tid":1936520,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T09:28:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4ecb6c493203396b5c49e38908be32268ca0972","tid":1936520,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T09:28:57.000Z","msg":"唔知當時大家做緊乜呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"735f66351ac10943ebed4682509d379e82158d07","tid":1936520,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T09:29:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa